mhealthatlas-users 0.0.1-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers contains all functionalities of the mHealthAtlas user service.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.command
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config contains the service configuration.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.kafka
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.kafka contains the kafka specific configuration of the service.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.web
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.web contains the web specific configuration of the service.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.web.filter
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.config.web contains the definition of custom filter used in the filter pipeline for HTTP requests.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.controller
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the mHealthAtlas user service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the information state.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.dto
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.model
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.model contains all entities from the mHealthAtlas user service database and the enum declarations.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.properties
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.properties contains the custom service properties.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.query
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.receiver
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.receiver contains all kafka event listener.
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.repository
com.mhealthatlas.mhealthatlasusers.repository contains all repository interfaces of the mHealthAtlas user service.
